UNITED STATES of America v. ONE LA SALLE SEDAN AUTOMOBILE, Motor No. 22432. No. 6256. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Sept. 15, 1930.

Before DIETRICH and WILBUR, Circuit Judges, and WEBSTER, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to stipulation, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
